## PillPals environment example
##
## Copy to `.env` (NOT committed) if you use flutter_dotenv.
## This repo ignores `.env` via `.gitignore`.
##
## Backend base URL. Loaded at startup (see `lib/main.dart`). Precedence:
## 1) `flutter run --dart-define=API_BASE_URL=...` 2) this file 3) http://127.0.0.1:8000
##
## On a real device, 127.0.0.1 is the phone itself. Use your Mac’s LAN IP, e.g.:
##   API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.12:8000
API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

